@startuml
!include ../_style.puml

title UC-02: Login

actor User
participant "Entry-Hub" as EH <<service>>
participant "Security-Switch" as SS <<service>>
participant "Database-Vault" as DV <<service>>
participant "Network-Manager" as NM <<service>>

User -> EH : POST /api/login (HTTPS)\nemail, password
EH -> SS : forward request (mTLS)
SS -> DV : forward request (mTLS)

note over EH, DV
  Each hop independently re-validates the input (DV-F-02).
  On failure: HTTP 400, request not forwarded further,
  issue logged without identifying the user (EH-F-06, SS-F-03, DV-F-20)
end note

DV -> DV : retrieve salt via SHA-256(email)\nrecompute Argon2id(password, salt, pepper)\ncompare with stored hash

alt nonexistent email or wrong password
  DV --> SS : 401 Unauthorized
  SS --> EH : 401 Unauthorized
  EH --> User : 401 Unauthorized
else valid credentials
  DV --> SS : authentication success
  SS -> NM : grant ACL tag, 12h expiry (mTLS)
  NM --> SS : ACL grant confirmed
  SS --> EH : 200 OK
  EH --> User : 200 OK
end

@enduml
